sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>mTLS
    participant DSCCtrl as DataScienceCluster<br/>Controller
    participant GitHub as github.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Components as Component Resources<br/>(Dashboard, KServe, etc.)

    Note over User,Components: Flow 1: Component Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply -f dsc.yaml<br/>Auth: kubeconfig credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-opendatahub-io-v1<br/>TLS 1.2+ API Server mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-opendatahub-io-v1<br/>TLS 1.2+ API Server mTLS<br/>(set defaults)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutation Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: DataScienceCluster CR created

    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification<br/>DataScienceCluster changed
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: CR Spec

    DSCCtrl->>GitHub: GET manifest files<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>No Auth
    GitHub-->>DSCCtrl: Component manifests (YAML)

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply component resources<br/>(Deployments, Services, CRs)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Components: Create/Update resources
    Components-->>K8sAPI: Resources created

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update DataScienceCluster status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR status updated

    Note over User,Components: Flow 2: Platform Initialization

    participant DSCICtrl as DSCInitialization<br/>Controller
    participant Monitoring as Monitoring Namespace<br/>Resources

    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>(on operator startup)
    K8sAPI->>DSCICtrl: Watch notification

    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create monitoring namespace<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCICtrl: Namespace created

    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy monitoring resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Monitoring: ServiceMonitors, ConfigMaps
    Monitoring-->>K8sAPI: Resources ready

    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Configure service mesh<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Inject trusted CA bundles<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Update DSCInitialization status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Components: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(monitoring namespace)
    participant AuthProxy as Auth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Manager as Operator Manager<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Prometheus->>AuthProxy: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    AuthProxy->>AuthProxy: Validate RBAC<br/>(check get on /metrics)
    AuthProxy->>Manager: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (internal pod)
    Manager-->>AuthProxy: Prometheus metrics
    AuthProxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics (HTTPS)
